import { Link } from "react-router-dom" function PlayerProfile(props) { const playerData = props.playerData // const countryCAP = playerData?.playerInformation?.[4].countryCode // const country = countryCAP.toLowerCase console.log(playerData) return ( <>
{playerData.name}
{playerData.primaryTeam?.teamName}
{/*
{playerData?.positionDescription?.primaryPosition?.label}
*/}
{playerData.injuryInformation && <>
{playerData?.injuryInformation?.name} | {playerData?.injuryInformation?.expectedReturn?.expectedReturnFallback}
}
{playerData?.playerInformation?.[0]?.value?.fallback}
